'''''Exiles of the Force''''' was a four-part comic miniseries proposed by [[Jim Baikie]] to [[Dark Horse Comics]] in [[1996]] that would have [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] and [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo]] dealing with a new [[The Force/Legends|Force]]-related threat. It was apparently going to be a prequel to ''[[Heart of the Jedi]]'' and ''[[Legacy of Doom]]''.

